\sin^2\alpha
\int_0^{\pi/2}\sqrt{a^2\sin^2 t+b^2\cos^2 t}dt\geq{\pi\over2}\sqrt{ab+(a-b)^2/\pi}\ .
a=\sqrt{2}\cos({\pi\over4}-\alpha)\ ,\quad b=\sqrt{2}\cos({\pi\over4}+\alpha)\qquad(0\leq\alpha\leq{\pi\over4}).
(a-b)^2=4\sin^2\alpha,\qquad ab =1-2\sin^2\alpha,
RHS={\pi\over2}\sqrt{1-(2-4/\pi)\sin^2\alpha}\leq {\pi\over2}-({\pi\over2}-1)\sin^2\alpha.\qquad(1)
a^2\sin^2 t+b^2\cos^2 t=1-\sin(2\alpha)\cos(2t)
LHS=\int_0^{\pi/2}{1\over2}\Bigl(\sqrt{1-\sin(2\alpha)\cos\tau}+\sqrt{1+\sin(2\alpha)\cos\tau}\Bigr)\ d\tau.
f(x):={1\over2}\bigl(\sqrt{1-x}+\sqrt{1+x}\bigr)\geq 1-{2x^2\over 15}-{x^4\over6}=:g(x)\qquad(0\leq x\leq 1),
LHS\geq \int_0^{\pi/2} g\bigl(\sin(2\alpha)\cos\tau\bigr)\  d\tau={\pi\over2}-{\pi\cos^2\alpha\over240}(47-15\cos\alpha)\sin^2\alpha.\qquad(2)
{\pi\cos^2\alpha\over240}(47-15\cos\alpha)\leq {\pi\over2}-1\qquad(0\leq\alpha\leq{\pi\over4}).
